<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="it">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8"/>
<title>Marker KANJI — Blé de Champagne</title>
<style>
  @page{size:A4;margin:12mm}
  *{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}
  body{font-family:Georgia,serif;background:white;display:flex;flex-direction:column;
       align-items:center;justify-content:center;min-height:100vh;gap:7mm;padding:10mm;text-align:center}
  h1{font-size:17pt;color:#5a7a10;letter-spacing:.06em}
  .sub{font-size:9pt;color:#666}
  .wrap{border:8mm solid black;padding:6mm;background:white;display:inline-block}
  .wrap img{display:block;width:120mm;height:120mm;image-rendering:pixelated}
  .badge{background:#5a7a10;color:white;font-size:7.5pt;letter-spacing:.2em;padding:2mm 7mm;text-transform:uppercase}
  .info{font-size:8.5pt;color:#444;line-height:1.9;border-top:1px solid #ccc;padding-top:5mm;max-width:145mm}
  .info b{color:#5a7a10;display:block;margin-bottom:1mm}
  @media print{.noprint{display:none}}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<h1>🌾 BLÉ DE CHAMPAGNE</h1>
<div class="sub">Marker Kanji · Camera AR · Inquadra con la fotocamera</div>
<div class="wrap">
  <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Marker Kanji AR.js"/>
</div>
<div class="badge">MARKER KANJI — AR.js preset</div>
<div class="info">
  <b>Come usare:</b>
  1. Stampa in bianco e nero su carta A4 — non plastificare<br>
  2. Apri la Camera AR dal sito<br>
  3. Tieni il foglio fermo su piano orizzontale<br>
  4. Distanza fotocamera: 20–40 cm · buona illuminazione
</div>
<button class="noprint" onclick="window.print()"
  style="padding:8px 24px;background:#5a7a10;color:white;border:none;
         font-size:10pt;cursor:pointer;font-family:Georgia,serif;margin-top:3mm">
  🖨 Stampa
</button>
</body>
</html>
